  "title": "All-Party Parliamentary Group on Sustainable Finance",
  "purpose": "The APPG’s aim is to develop and advocate for policies which promote environmentally responsible financial practices while ensuring economic stability. Its focus is not only on driving long-term investment in sustainability but also on fostering a financial system that is transparent and accountable. We are non-partisan and work to build consensus across the political spectrum to create a greener, more equitable future.",
